#\\__//¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//
        Elevate-Script ; Display-TrueColors ; Make-Decision     #//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\__//¯¯\\
